    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
