      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>chicken breast strips<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>dried oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 15-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
