    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> to the <strong>peppers</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 10-12 min or until the sauce has thickened</p>",
      "order": 6,
